type: dataset
date-released: 2026-04-01
url: "https://github.com/NickGillArizona/Displacing-Deference-Data-and-Doctrine-for-a-Disability-Centered-AFFH"
repository-code: "https://github.com/NickGillArizona/Displacing-Deference-Data-and-Doctrine-for-a-Disability-Centered-AFFH"
abstract: >-
  Replication package for a Note demonstrating that HUD's
  administrative choices — guidance rescission, FHIP defunding, and zero
  reasonable-cause charges — created the disability fair housing enforcement
  crisis. Contains the FHA Unified Database (2,522 screened-in federal FHA
  cases; 1,720 disability), the first published race-by-disability housing
  cost-burden cross-tabulations, classification pipeline documentation, Census
  PUMS analysis scripts, and supplementary appendices.
keywords:
  - fair housing act
  - disability
  - AFFH
